original: Falk, Ade, hypoteksombudsman, Linköping, f. 7/6/05 i Uppsala av överste Per F. o. Märta Schröder. G. 40 m. Ulla Gibson. Barn: Eva f. 41, Carin 43. — Stud:ex. v. Upps. h. a. 1. 24, jur. kand. i Upps. 31. Tingstjg. i Linköp. doms. 32-35, e. länsbokhåll. i östérgötl. 1. 37-41, omb :man i Ostgöta Hypoteksfören. sed. 42.
translated: Falk, Ade, mortgage attorney, Linköping, born on June 7th, 1905 in Uppsala to Colonel Per F. and Märta Schröder. Married to Ulla Gibson in 1940 and has two children: Eva (born 1941) and Carin (born 1943). Completed high school studies at Uppsala in 1924 and earned a law degree from Uppsala University in 1931. Served as a court clerk in Linköping from 1932 to 1935, then as a county bookkeeper in Östergötland from 1937 to 1941. Became a representative for Ostgöta Mortgage Association in 1942.
